					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Right, the APU frame counter in mode $4017=$00 cycles through every 29830 CPU clocks. But why does this matter for sound generation? Overall timing should be based on PPU frames, with the APU simply running however many CPU clocks that frame happened to be. There's no reason for the APU's "frames" (which have no relation to PPU frames) to play a part in any overall timing.</div>

